{"tid":2119088,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"杭州女追劇 驚見自家別墅被盜用","createTime":"2020-07-22T02:07:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T02:27:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"30afacc5b72b80e6c7aee3d32347824fc2ff3771","tid":2119088,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:07:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200722/IPBA7CI2PZFBTUPXXA4CVANGBQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200722%2FIPBA7CI2PZFBTUPXXA4CVANGBQ%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB0Ka%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=f8da3757\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200722%2FIPBA7CI2PZFBTUPXXA4CVANGBQ%2F&h=33e80daf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200722/IPBA7CI2PZFBTUPXXA4CVANGBQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n杭州女追劇 驚見自家別墅被盜用<br />\n<br />\n杭州一名林姓女士，五年前在家鄉慈溪市買了一棟豪華別墅，但一直沒回去住過。豈料去年在煲劇期間，發現自家別墅成了劇中女主角的家，更睡在自己床上。她一氣之下將物業管理、電視劇出品方告上法院。不過更讓她意想不到的是，在她別墅內取景的電視劇竟不止一部。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3-BNYcjo6ZIqMmaVScc5kLkxx2o=/640x645/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UF4RGCMF33UFBGEGT5COBSMYME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3-BNYcjo6ZIqMmaVScc5kLkxx2o%3D%2F640x645%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUF4RGCMF33UFBGEGT5COBSMYME.jpg&h=e69e5281&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n杭州一名女子不知情下，五年未住的豪宅被用來拍劇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n怒告劇組物業管理<br />\n<br />\n林女在2015年買下的別墅相當豪華，採用歐式設計，包括地面四層、地下一層，還設有酒窖和藏寶室。但林女一開始已考慮到可能長期不住，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n林女隨後回到別墅，發現屋內電梯損壞無法啟動，奢侈品絲巾及全部地毯污損，。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n在第一次庭審中，林女得悉因另一部。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《錢江晚報》"},{"pid":"56a66860661cd78ee0f12dda5fec2035cd09d919","tid":2119088,"uid":108017,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedB